			<div class="meta clear">
				<p>From &rarr; <a href="https://micfic.wordpress.com/category/submissions/volume-ii/20100920-to-20101003-ghost/" rel="category tag">2010/09/20 to 2010/10/03 - Ghost</a>, <a href="https://micfic.wordpress.com/category/feedback/constructive-criticism/" rel="category tag">Constructive criticism</a>, <a href="https://micfic.wordpress.com/category/submissions/volume-ii/" rel="category tag">Volume II</a></p>
